{"tid":1132691,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"土耳其總統艾爾段 : 沒有土耳其F-35計畫註定失敗","createTime":"2019-04-30T13:14:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-30T14:58:59.000Z","uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"cfd8cc0b7c1a49b677e70f24af22ad1a57659f52","tid":1132691,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T13:14:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/WyuMW9VyAsO70saWfhM6pA--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MzYw/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-TW/homerun/rti.org.tw/7e40c99140d1a6a52c1fc9b1fab6f559\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FWyuMW9VyAsO70saWfhM6pA--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MzYw%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-TW%2Fhomerun%2Frti.org.tw%2F7e40c99140d1a6a52c1fc9b1fab6f559&h=ad38cbab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n土耳其總理艾爾段(Recep Tayyip Erdogan)(資料照片/AFP)<br />\n<br />\n土耳其總統艾爾段(Tayyip Erdogan)今天(30日)說，包括土耳其在內、多國參與的F-35匿蹤戰鬥機開發計畫，若是沒有土國的參與將註定失敗。艾爾段並說，土國受到不公平的對待。<br />\n<br />\n因為土耳其計畫向俄國購買S-400防空飛彈，與美國的關係陷入緊張。白宮指若是將F-35交付給土國，將會危及這款第五代戰機的安全，美方並威脅說，若是土國堅持購買S-400防空飛彈，也會危及安卡拉繼續參與F-35戰機的開發計畫，並且恐怕會遭美國國會制裁。美國已暫停交付土耳其F-35戰機，以及相關訓練設備和零件。<br />\n<br />\n土國不僅是F-35戰機的潛在買家，也是這款新式戰機的開發夥伴之一。除了土國，美國、英國、義大利、荷蘭、加拿大、澳洲、丹麥和挪威也都是這款戰機的夥伴國家。<br />\n<br />\n艾爾段今天在出席一場國防工會博覽會時表示，那些想要將土耳其排除在F-35計畫之外的人，並沒有深思熟慮，若是如此將會讓F-35計畫走向失敗，他並指安卡拉正加快腳步，發展自己的國防系統。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E8%89%BE%E7%88%BE%E6%AE%B5%E5%97%86%E8%81%B2-%E6%B2%92%E6%9C%89%E5%9C%9F%E8%80%B3%E5%85%B6f-35%E8%A8%88%E7%95%AB%E8%A8%BB%E5%AE%9A%E5%A4%B1%E6%95%97-113340720.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E8%2589%25BE%25E7%2588%25BE%25E6%25AE%25B5%25E5%2597%2586%25E8%2581%25B2-%25E6%25B2%2592%25E6%259C%2589%25E5%259C%259F%25E8%2580%25B3%25E5%2585%25B6f-35%25E8%25A8%2588%25E7%2595%25AB%25E8%25A8%25BB%25E5%25AE%259A%25E5%25A4%25B1%25E6%2595%2597-113340720.html&d=jZUVzsr%2BlXwf2hbAbvJm1RPX6nNrjY8iteK6A9FjwF0%3D&h=db8e71e8\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E8%89%BE%E7%88%BE%E6%AE%B5%E5%97%86%E8%81%B2-%E6%B2%92%E6%9C%89%E5%9C%9F%E8%80%B3%E5%85%B6f-35%E8%A8%88%E7%95%AB%E8%A8%BB%E5%AE%9A%E5%A4%B1%E6%95%97-113340720.html</a>"},{"pid":"63ecff47b9ca7e859152de3cb2d43bfa1c3b2c2a","tid":1132691,"uid":192158,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T13:16:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4d21d6318fd58913aa860ffd75bb61e6ad6d3ca8","tid":1132691,"uid":27688,"like":1,"dislike":10,"score":-9,"quote":{"pid":"63ecff47b9ca7e859152de3cb2d43bfa1c3b2c2a","tid":1132691,"uid":192158,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T13:16:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T13:17:49.000Z","msg":"我只識程美段唔識艾爾段"},{"pid":"6e450de5dfd03c9f6bf670174d956447fd006477","tid":1132691,"uid":210121,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T13:37:33.000Z","msg":"幾時對支共發動聖戰？"},{"pid":"679685f3e58d0ae6591b28a6a765f61db466586d","tid":1132691,"uid":47259,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T14:19:34.000Z","msg":"把自己看得這麼高.jpg<br />\n同支那屎為話唔用佢就失敗有乜分别<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec26b6804eb42eb9678171e97f2f82e5b8afff23","tid":1132691,"uid":61271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T14:24:55.000Z","msg":"土耳其繼續左右不是人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccbf76e9ed955f5b4b139261c495d71f4585b9f1","tid":1132691,"uid":165187,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T14:29:37.000Z","msg":"火雞=rubbish <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"021869fcfb189397bf01f5007521048f1e3e5cdd","tid":1132691,"uid":52946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T14:30:54.000Z","msg":"想食2家茶禮邊有咁著